description: Spacious and beautiful studio located in the sought-after Mayfair Tower, just steps from Piedmont Park, Colony Square, the High Museum, and Midtown’s premier dining, shopping, and entertainment. Enjoy sweeping city views, including the Buckhead skyline, from this high-rise gem.    This unit features an extra-large built-in wall bed, a modern walk-in shower, and a generous kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and elegant cabinetry. Building amenities include a serene courtyard with grills, a library, club room, fitness center, and 24-hour concierge service.    Extras included: Internet (provided by the building), in-unit washer/dryer, and trash service.    Investor-friendly: No rental cap. Excellent opportunity for both investors and homeowners.    Live, work, or invest in the heart of it all – walk to everything Midtown has to offer!
